			<h4><a id="comment_link_64250768" name="comment_link_64250768" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23231052&amp;cid=64250768" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64250768)" >Re:Is it?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64250768" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64250768); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Tx">Tx</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Tx">( 96709 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64250768">		
