			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64251878">		
		on Monday February 19, 2024 @01:00PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23231052&amp;cid=64251878">#64251878</a>)
