			<h4><a id="comment_link_64250996" name="comment_link_64250996" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23231052&amp;cid=64250996" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64250996)" >A wild guess</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64250996" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64250996); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
